<h1>Installation</h1>

<p>
  To install Design System you can use <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://docs.npmjs.com/">Yarn</a>:
</p>
<pre>yarn add @fandom/design-system</pre>

<section>
  <h2>How to install SVG</h2>
  <p>
    Read more about how to handle SVG on {{#link-to "overview.svg-assets"}}SVG Assets{{/link-to}} page.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>How to install SCSS</h2>
  <p>This is a preferred way of using Design System as this installs both styles and variables.</p>
  <p>
    To use SCSS files in your project include
    <a
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      href="https://github.com/Wikia/design-system/blob/master/dist/scss/index.scss"
    >
      dist/scss/index.scss
    </a>
    in your main SCSS file:

    <Demo @name="path-to-design-system" @language="scss" @codeOnly={{true}}>
      @import "path/to/@fandom/design-system/dist/scss/index"
    </Demo>

    Note that
    <a
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      href="https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer"
    >
      autoprefixer
    </a> is required for SCSS compilation,
    as there are no prefixes in SCSS files.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>How to install CSS</h2>
  <p>
    If you can"t use SASS or prefer to use CSS, you can include
    <a
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      href="https://github.com/Wikia/design-system/blob/master/dist/css/styles.css"
    >
      dist/css/styles.css
    </a>
    in your project:
  </p>
  <pre>path/to/@fandom/design-system/dist/css/styles.css</pre>
  <p>
    Note that compiled CSS for Design System include prefixes managed by autoprefixer and
    targets 4 last versions of major browsers. As configured here:
    <a
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      href="https://github.com/Wikia/design-system/blob/master/ember-cli-build.js"
    >
      ember-cli-build.js
    </a>
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>How to include SASS variables</h2>
  <p>This step is not needed if you import SCSS files.</p>
  <p>
    To import SASS variables import
    <a
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      href="https://github.com/Wikia/design-system/blob/master/dist/scss/wds-variables/index.scss"
    >
      dist/scss/wds-variables/index.scss
    </a>:
    <Demo @name="path-to-variables" @language="scss" @codeOnly={{true}}>
      @import "path/to/@fandom/design-system/dist/scss/wds-variables/index"
    </Demo>
  </p>
</section>
